'From Squeakland 3.8.5976 of 25 August 2004 [latest update: #278] on 31 August 2004 at 6:54:51 pm'!"Change Set:		FlapTranslucentLabelFix-nkDate:			31 August 2004Author:			Ned KonzThis is a fix for the labels on the flaps having a green background.I had fixed these labels, but apparently in the 0269dblTranslations-dgd change set the fix was broken again.For the labels to be the right color, the flap has to be colored first."!!PartsBin class methodsFor: 'instance creation' stamp: 'nk 8/31/2004 18:51'!newPartsBinWithOrientation: aListDirection andColor: aColor from: quadList 	"Answer a new PartBin object, to run horizontally or vertically,  	obtaining its elements from the list of tuples of the form:  	(<receiver> <selector> <label> <balloonHelp>)"	^ (self new)		color: aColor;		listDirection: aListDirection quadList: (self translatedQuads: quadList).! !